# Todos App
The Todos App is a simple web application built with React using Vite, which allows users to manage their to-do lists.

![App Screenshot](./public/screenshot.jpeg)

## Features
The app provides the following features:

- Add new tasks to the to-do list
- Mark tasks as completed
- Delete tasks from the to-do list

## Installation
To use the Todos App, you need to clone the code to your local machine using the following command:

```bash
git clone https://github.com/AckylaFB/todos.git
```
After cloning the code, navigate to the project's directory and run the following commands to install dependencies and run the app:

```bash
yarn install
yarn dev
```

## Usage
To add a new task, type the task description in the input field and click on Add Todo. To mark a task as completed, click on the checkbox next to the task description. To delete a task, click on the delete button next to the task.


